---
const blogUrl = 'https://joannjoneswalczak.blogspot.com/';
---
<section id="blog" class="py-16 md:py-24 scroll-mt-20 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-soft" style="animation-delay: 0.35s">
  <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-paper mb-4">Blog</h2>
    <p class="text-paper/80 text-lg mb-8">
      On Layton: The View from My Front Porch—stories, reflections, and conversations from the blog that led to the book.
    </p>
    <a href={blogUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent text-ink font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-hover transition-all duration-350 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl active:scale-[0.98]">
      Read the blog
      <span class="ml-2" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
